    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔法纪元席卷了自由地：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 帮助野法师互助会的现任领导者阿德琳娜，实现她的野心，将魔法引入到自由地的角斗赛事中。在这场新的巨大变革中获利，培养你的魔法角斗士，战胜同样受到魔法加持对手，取得更辉光的成就，洗刷家族的屈辱。大约2个小时的额外故事线，包括两个精心设计的关卡，一段神秘而浪漫的剧情。神秘的魔法力量将在剧情中大放异彩！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/dffcc376f8ff8e20a341f8e7d0f46cb7.poster.avif?t=1734032248\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/dffcc376f8ff8e20a341f8e7d0f46cb7.webm?t=1734032248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 一个全新的魔法主题角斗场和它的魔法冠军。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/c3fac037d7aad241c4a873db6ec51da0.poster.avif?t=1734032248\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/c3fac037d7aad241c4a873db6ec51da0.webm?t=1734032248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 6系的魔法流派，共计60个全新的法术技能。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/0e36ed85e2861482261dbdea7e478da9.poster.avif?t=1734032248\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/0e36ed85e2861482261dbdea7e478da9.webm?t=1734032248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>火焰：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暴躁和热烈的火焰魔法，给你的对手带来巨大的伤害，并将他们点燃！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>冰霜：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冷酷的冰霜魔法可以对敌人造成中量伤害，并严重限制他们的行动。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>闪电：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用闪电的力量伤害敌人，或者强化自己，闪电系魔法擅长造成大范围的连锁伤害。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>空气：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用大气的力量操纵你的敌人，令他们陷于不利的境地，或化解他们的攻势。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>光明：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用光明的力量保护自己与盟友，提高抗性并恢复生命值，也可以对敌人造成一定伤害。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗：</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用黑暗的力量腐化和伤害你的敌人，对其造成可怕的直接伤害，或将它们弱化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 海量法师的武器和装备，其中不乏有着独特效果的传奇装备！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/c4792cb21297bb1f94021c73ab14bf27.poster.avif?t=1734032248\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282660/extras/c4792cb21297bb1f94021c73ab14bf27.webm?t=1734032248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
